name: San Antonio Women Demoing Robotics
description:
Ladies, let's crash the SVR Bots'n'Beer!
Tonight all the great demos are from amazing women in robotics!

  • SWRI
  • Plus One Robotics
  • Renubot
  • ReckonPoint
  • ???
More about Silicon Valley Robotics Bots&Beer:
We do announcements, introductions, demos and tech discussions. Would you like to speak? Showcase a robot? Join the organizing team? bots&beer@svrobo.org

We're also starting in person Bots&Beer events and Robotics Open Houses in the SV/SF Bay Area and beyond, so check the Silicon Valley Robotics calendar https://svrobo.org/calendar
OR sign up for our newsletter https://getrevue.co/profile/svrobo

Silicon Valley Robotics is more than just a meetup. If you are a robotics startup or company you can join our organization at https://svrobo.org/membership

name: WiR Organizers & Volunteers Get Together
description:
If you're helping Women in Robotics or interested in volunteering then this meeting is for you. 
Let's create more local chapters and events, more online activities, more stories and inspiring content. Bring your ideas, your enthusiasm and your questions.
